{"tid":2151973,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)我係四號仔 麻辣黑幫","createTime":"2020-08-11T16:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T17:32:18.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b94fc6c7a58906c60ba532e06b6f9dceb34ba2d","tid":2151973,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=b3d1a9c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=25eee45c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/62/I_Am_Number_Four_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F6%2F62%2FI_Am_Number_Four_Poster.jpg&h=a80441a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/75/The_Family_2013%2C_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F75%2FThe_Family_2013%252C_Poster.jpg&h=42ddb41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一名來自羅瑞恩行星的外星人（艾力克斯&middot;派帝佛 飾）為了逃離一群來自摩加多利恩行星，摧毀他們故鄉的侵略者，在孩提時代與另外八名同伴被送往了地球。在他身邊有一名守護者（提摩西&middot;奧力芬 飾）負責保護他的生命安全，而他本身的能力也漸漸覺醒，像是力氣增強、超快速度、善靈敏度、心靈傳動能力、能對抗高熱與火焰，以及從手掌中發光及發出脈衝<br />\n<br />\n2.講述一個原名為曼佐尼（Manzoni）、處於「證人保護計劃」下的黑手黨家庭遷居到諾曼第後、更名為布雷克（Blake），開始努力適應新生活的故事<br />\n<br />\n1 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=5600e4c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=e0399e74\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebc219645f49c538af3c235976ab912355fd54e","tid":2151973,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=48d5ffc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵"},{"pid":"eeb7297ec3ba8c8b19be585941f6a70d924f5500","tid":2151973,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de4ffb